<br>
Oh, and the sneak working on everything.... Well, sortof yes, sortof no.<br>
<br>
From a monk's perspective, sneak will cut the aggro radius of just about everything. There are a couple of exceptions I've seen out in the planes, but they could be written off as me having aggro before I knew it, coming up from a feign or something.<br>
<br>
Being able to get RIGHT UP behind something isn't universal, I don't think. You can get a lot closer than you should be able to in all cases, I think. But sneak making you indiff and non-aggro as long as you're behind them right up to the backs of their very feet I'm not totally convinced of. Either way, sneak's more useful than Hide (in my experience) unless you're a rogue and can do both at once and move.<br>
<br>
Oh, and I'm pretty sure halfling sneak/hide is in the mid thirties. Check your skill list. It'll be something like below average, bad, or very bad. It won't be awful (I don't think) which would be what a 1 would show as. Though I was really, really amused at the auction of a weapon from Luclin that gave +1 sneak being touted as giving the unskilled the ability to do it. At THAT skill level, you'd never get a success when you wanted it.<br>
<br>
Sutekh<br>
Twilight Requiem <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#112512><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/ulannellavelglarn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lannella Velglarn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/hottopic.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse & Amway Rep.</span><br>  Posts: 472<br> <font color=#CCCCC8>(12/18/01 6:00:17 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.strike9.com/eq/Lannella/fullsize/headshot3.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: only....</span><hr size=1> Kokuten did say he'd just be a *sneaky* bastard.  I think he gets it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I think you hit the nail on the head about planar (ie) agro.  Some mobs have humungous agro ranges, and I've heard there will sometimes be an effect of social agro being passed off from a mob (that you can't see yet but can see you sneaking), and the mob you think you're sneaking behind.  Also, since being close to walls can get one spotted by what behind the wall agro-wise, that can pass agro to what you're behind as well.  A number of ways that Sneak can *seem* to fail, but it's circumstantial. <br>
<br>
Granted, I've not gone planar yet, but I've taken advantage of my tourist abilities.  I have gone right up beside (past the shoes) of red SeeInvis mobs without agro.  Arc of sight of mobs covers *less* than 90 degrees from center, somewhere around 75ish.  You can experiment with a KoS mob from a safe distance - start sneaking even with their side and you'll con them as Indiff.  Move parallel and forward and you'll see that at a certain point you go from Indiff to KoS.  That's their line of sight.  If you're so close behind them that you pass whatever VI counts as their 'center' then that might put you 'into' their view.<br>
<br>
As far as the Luclin stuff goes, I've yet to hear about a sneak/hide/picklocks item that is actually useful.  They all add so little as to be useless at the level at which they can be obtained.  They also don't seem to put you beyond your level cap anyway (proved that last night with Mech lockpicks (2%) when I couldn't pick the FP bank). <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.showMessage?topicID=1782.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.showMessage?topicID=1759.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.emailToFriend?topicID=1778.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.threadControl?topicID=1778.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1778.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1778.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub16.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="druzzilro86846generaldiscussion">General Discussion<option value